# Generated artifacts (transient logs ignored by default; phase25 cluster
# outputs, SLURM-run logs auto-pushed by cluster/*.slurm, and .gitkeep
# markers are tracked)
logs/*
!logs/.gitkeep
!logs/phase25/
!logs/patrl18smoke_*
!logs/bench14_*

# CCDS canonical (Phase 26 Wave 3): models/ contents gitignored (heavy
# artifacts); tracked via .gitkeep markers. reports/ is tracked (small
# CSV/MD outputs are paper-ready and version-worthy). Cluster auto-push
# subtrees (patrl_smoke/, power/) are whitelisted so SLURM auto-push
# commits land. Uses models/* + !subdir pattern (NOT bare models/) so
# subdirectory whitelists work — bare models/ with trailing slash blocks
# any subdir re-include per git-ignore semantics.
models/*
results/*
!models/.gitkeep
!models/mle/.gitkeep
!models/bayesian/.gitkeep
!models/patrl_smoke/
!models/power/

# GSD planning audit trail — local-only, not pushed (per user policy)
.planning/

# Data (not committed - too large / sensitive)
data/*
# ...but viz_fixtures/ ships schema-round-trip inputs (Phase 22+) -- commit them
!data/viz_fixtures/

